Landslide Prediction: Regression & Classification
This project builds machine learning models to predict landslides.

Regression Task
Target: Rainfall_mm
Models: Linear Regression, Random Forest
Optimization: Hyperparameter tuning

Classification Task
Target: landslide_size
Models: Decision Tree, Random Forest
Optimization: GridSearchCV, Recursive Feature Elimination

Evaluation
Metrics: RMSE, MAE (Regression), Accuracy, ClassificationReport, Confusion Matrix (Classification)

Requirements
Python, Scikit-learn, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib
